description: We specialize in our version of a Rochester NY culinary creation: Our All Fired Up Plate. This amazing mixture of flavors includes a hamburger and a hot dog on top of a selection of 2 choices of macaroni salad, baked beans, or seasoned home fries. This amazing dish is then topped with a spicy meat sauce made from spices and slowly simmered ground beef, garnished with onions, and served with a roll. Along with our plate we have a variety of changing items which include soup of the day, a variety of lunch combo platters, appetizers, and fresh filled cannolis. Come by today and try the taste sensation for yourself!
name: All Fired Up Concessions
